# Gotchas ‚Äî where the pandas API ends

## Close to pandas, not identical

- **Row order** ‚Äî not guaranteed unless `sort_index()` / `sort_values()`
- **Lazy, not eager** ‚Äî only actions execute
- **`inplace=True`** ‚Äî often ignored (Spark DataFrames are immutable)
- **`iterrows` / `apply(axis=1)` w/o type hint** ‚Äî pull to driver / sample schema ‚Äî slow
- **`df.loc[missing]`** ‚Äî may return empty, not `KeyError`
- Some methods ‚Üí **`PandasNotImplementedError`**

## Two settings

- **`compute.ops_on_diff_frames`** ‚Äî `False` by default ‚Üí combining two frames errors (alignment needs a shared index)
- **`compute.default_index_type`** ‚Äî from the last section
